---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import ChatbotToggle from "../components/ChatbotToggle.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <slot slot="title">Michael Cabrera | USRad</slot>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-28 bg-[#f0f4f9] text-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center space-y-7">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold text-[#003087]">
        Michael Cabrera
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-[#e6c378] font-medium">Founder & CEO</p>
      <div class="h-1 w-32 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Bio Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-16">
      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-10">
        <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <img
            src="/images/michael.jpg"
            alt="Michael Cabrera"
            class="w-full object-cover"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#003087]/80 to-transparent h-24"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Highlights -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div
            class="bg-[#f9f9f6] p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all"
          >
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087] mb-4 flex items-center"
            >
              <span class="w-2 h-8 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-3"></span> Highlights
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-3">
              <li>Built imaging networks serving 400,000+ patients</li>
              <li>
                Selected for MIT‚Äôs ‚ÄúBirthing of Giants‚Äù ‚Äî global top 0.25%
              </li>
              <li>
                Scaled operations nationwide and led successful public exit
              </li>
              <li>Known for people-first leadership and execution clarity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Impact -->
          <div
            class="bg-[#f9f9f6] p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all text-center"
          >
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087] mb-4 flex justify-center items-center"
            >
              <span class="w-2 h-8 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-3"></span> Impact
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-4xl font-semibold text-[#003087] hover:text-[#002b7a] transition-colors"
            >
              400,000+
            </p>
            <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mx-auto my-4"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Imaging procedures delivered under Michael‚Äôs leadership ‚Äî each one
              a step toward earlier diagnosis, clearer answers, and better
              outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Press Kit -->
          <div class="text-center pt-6">
            <a
              href="/docs/founder-presskit.pdf"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-block bg-[#003087] text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#00256e] transition-all hover:shadow-lg w-full border-l-4 border-[#e6c378] font-medium"
            >
              Download Press Kit
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column -->
      <div
        class="md:col-span-2 space-y-10 text-gray-700 text-xl leading-relaxed"
      >
        <p>
          Michael Cabrera‚Äôs journey began at 13, delivering newspapers after
          school on a red Raleigh bicycle. That early hustle turned into a
          lifelong drive to solve big problems in healthcare‚Äîwith a belief that
          access and empathy aren‚Äôt mutually exclusive.
        </p>
        <p>
          Over the past two decades, Michael has helped shape how patients
          experience diagnostic care, leading with the conviction that systems
          work best when they‚Äôre built around people. He brings that same
          approach to USRad: thoughtful growth, radical simplicity, and
          relentless follow-through.
        </p>
        <p>
          Michael was selected for ‚ÄúBirthing of Giants,‚Äù a one-week-a-year
          program co-created by MIT, Inc. Magazine, and YEO (now EO), designed
          for the world‚Äôs fastest-growing entrepreneurs. Limited to just 60
          founders annually, the program helped him scale teams, modernize
          operations, and expand nationwide ‚Äî culminating in a successful public
          exit.
        </p>

        <blockquote
          class="border-l-4 border-[#E6C378] pl-8 py-6 italic text-2xl text-gray-600 my-12 bg-[#f9f9f6] pr-8 rounded-r-xl shadow-md"
        >
          "Looking ahead, I‚Äôm focused on building systems that scale ‚Äî without
          trading empathy for efficiency."
        </blockquote>

        <!-- Mission / Vision / Promise -->
        <div class="pt-12 border-t border-gray-200">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-medium text-[#003087] mb-8 flex items-center"
          >
            <span class="w-2 h-10 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-3"></span>
            Creating the Future of Medical Imaging
          </h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10">
            <div
              class="bg-[#f9f9f6] p-7 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all h-full"
            >
              <h3
                class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087] mb-3 flex items-center"
              >
                <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                Our Mission
              </h3>
              <p>
                To radically improve access to affordable, high-quality medical
                imaging ‚Äî with transparency, empathy, and innovation at the core
                of every interaction.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="bg-[#f9f9f6] p-7 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all h-full"
            >
              <h3
                class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087] mb-3 flex items-center"
              >
                <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                Our Vision
              </h3>
              <p>
                A future where no patient delays care due to confusion, cost, or
                access ‚Äî and where imaging centers thrive by aligning around
                shared values.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="bg-[#f9f9f6] p-7 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all h-full"
            >
              <h3
                class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087] mb-3 flex items-center"
              >
                <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                Our Promise
              </h3>
              <p>
                We treat every patient like family, offer honest pricing, and
                champion a care experience grounded in dignity, trust, and
                results.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Leadership Philosophy -->
        <div class="pt-12 border-t border-gray-200">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#003087] mb-6 flex items-center"
          >
            <span class="w-2 h-10 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-3"></span>
            Leadership Philosophy
          </h2>
          <p>
            My approach centers on building healthcare businesses that align the
            interests of all stakeholders ‚Äî ensuring patients receive
            exceptional care while providers focus on what they do best.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            By removing friction points and creating transparent systems, we've
            repeatedly demonstrated that the highest quality care can also be
            the most accessible and efficient.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact CTA -->
        <div class="pt-12">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block bg-[#003087] text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-[#00256e] transition-all hover:shadow-lg border-l-4 border-[#e6c378]"
          >
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Awards Section (unchanged from your original, or can be dropped in below here) -->

  <!-- Awards & Recognition Section -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#f0f4f9]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl font-semibold text-center text-[#003087] mb-16 flex items-center justify-center"
      >
        <span class="w-2 h-10 bg-[#e6c378] rounded-full mr-3"></span>
        Leadership Recognition
      </h2>

      <!-- Featured Award -->
      <div
        class="mb-20 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#e6c378]/30"
      >
        <div
          class="relative h-72 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-[#f0f4f9] flex items-center justify-center text-center px-6"
        >
          <div>
            <img
              src="/images/awards/inc500-logo.png"
              alt="Inc 500"
              class="h-40 mx-auto mb-4"
            />
            <p class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800">
              Fastest Growing Private Companies
            </p>
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#003087] mt-3">
              #210 with 1,236% Growth
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Awards Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <!-- Hispanic Business Award -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-center"
        >
          <div
            class="w-24 h-24 bg-[#f8f8f8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/awards/hispanic-business-logo.png"
              alt="Hispanic Business"
              class="w-16 h-16 object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087]">
              Hispanic Business Magazine
            </h4>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">
              500 Largest Hispanic-Owned Companies
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium mt-2">#223 | #259 | #320</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Three Consecutive Years</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SFBJ 40 Under 40 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-center"
        >
          <div
            class="w-24 h-24 bg-[#f8f8f8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/awards/sfbj-logo.png"
              alt="SFBJ"
              class="w-16 h-16 object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087]">
              South Florida Business Journal
            </h4>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">40 Under 40 Awards</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium mt-2">#19</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">
              Recognizing Business Leadership Excellence
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SFBJ Up & Comers -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-center"
        >
          <div
            class="w-24 h-24 bg-[#f8f8f8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/awards/sfbj-logo.png"
              alt="SFBJ"
              class="w-16 h-16 object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087]">
              South Florida Business Journal
            </h4>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Up & Comers Award</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium mt-2">1st Place</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">11th Anniversary Edition</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- UF 100 Fastest Growing -->
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-center"
        >
          <div
            class="w-24 h-24 bg-[#f8f8f8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/awards/uf-logo.png"
              alt="University of Florida"
              class="w-16 h-16 object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#003087]">
              University of Florida
            </h4>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600">100 Fastest Growing Companies</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium mt-2">#49 | #89</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Two Consecutive Years</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer Note -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center text-gray-600 text-base">
        <p>
          Awards and recognition received for AnciCare PPO, a nationwide
          diagnostic imaging company founded and led by Michael Cabrera.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ChatbotToggle chatbotLabel="üí¨ Let's Talk" />
</MainLayout>
